WEBVTT

00:39.020 --> 00:40.360
May I be like the stars

00:40.380 --> 00:41.580
and you like the moon.

00:42.450 --> 00:43.670
As long as the world remains,

00:44.780 --> 00:45.780
so shall we.

01:01.720 --> 01:03.830
I only wish to stay with the one I love,

01:04.430 --> 01:06.060
watching every sunrise and sunset.

01:07.640 --> 01:09.370
I want to be with you forever.

01:13.620 --> 01:14.920
Eternals and demons walk different paths.

01:15.640 --> 01:17.480
You and she are ultimately different.

01:37.970 --> 01:39.600
Have you ever

01:40.220 --> 01:41.789
truly cared for me?

01:44.440 --> 01:45.250
No.

01:45.660 --> 01:46.360
Never.

01:54.650 --> 01:57.720
In this life and the next, through all lifetimes‚Ä¶

02:02.150 --> 02:03.310
May we live and die together,

02:04.400 --> 02:06.040
and share life and death as one.

02:41.710 --> 02:45.790
[Moonlight Mystique]

02:46.320 --> 02:49.980
[Episode 28]

03:03.480 --> 03:04.550
Master?

03:06.180 --> 03:08.720
What exactly happened at Cold Spring Palace?

03:08.820 --> 03:11.290
Why did Fan Yue suddenly attack it?

03:11.320 --> 03:12.410
I don't know, Master.

03:12.750 --> 03:14.160
At the time, the situation was dire,

03:14.180 --> 03:15.850
so I had no choice but to leave first.

03:16.300 --> 03:17.550
Leaving was for the best.

03:18.090 --> 03:19.820
Zhen Yu was defeated by Fan Yue

03:20.300 --> 03:21.780
and fled with severe injuries.

03:21.810 --> 03:23.840
This is already widely known.

03:23.860 --> 03:25.030
After this battle,

03:25.510 --> 03:28.870
Cold Spring Palace will surely remain in hiding for a while.

03:29.060 --> 03:31.490
You've had a hard time these days.

03:31.520 --> 03:33.090
Come back to Lanling with me.

03:33.160 --> 03:35.680
Your uncles have been missing you.

03:38.880 --> 03:40.160
What are you doing?

03:40.180 --> 03:41.660
Master, please save Fu Ling.

03:41.960 --> 03:43.210
Fu Ling?

03:43.250 --> 03:44.820
Zhen Yu's disciple?

03:44.850 --> 03:46.410
She's here now?

03:46.610 --> 03:47.490
Yes.

03:50.660 --> 03:51.890
You're out of your mind!

03:51.920 --> 03:54.470
How could you involve yourself with a demon?

03:54.500 --> 03:56.220
Fu Ling has saved me many times,

03:56.240 --> 03:57.870
even at the risk of punishment from Zhen Yu.

03:58.070 --> 03:59.430
Now, she has left Cold Spring

03:59.430 --> 04:00.560
and has no further ties with Zhen Yu.

04:00.870 --> 04:01.990
Please, Master, save her.

04:02.020 --> 04:03.810
Even if she has left Cold Spring,

04:03.830 --> 04:05.230
she is still a demon!

04:05.250 --> 04:06.840
How can you forget all the wrongs she's done

04:06.840 --> 04:08.670
just because you're feeling merciful now?

04:08.700 --> 04:10.070
She's not a demon!

04:11.410 --> 04:12.450
What are you saying?

04:12.720 --> 04:13.960
She's Bai Xi,

04:14.850 --> 04:16.290
Bai Xun's daughter,

04:16.839 --> 04:18.019
and Shuo's older sister.

04:19.529 --> 04:20.920
What's going on?

04:20.940 --> 04:22.140
10 years ago,

04:22.170 --> 04:23.900
Zhen Yu took Bai Xi from the Bai family,

04:24.130 --> 04:25.820
erased her memories,

04:25.850 --> 04:27.190
and infused her with demonic power,

04:27.220 --> 04:28.700
turning her into a demon.

04:29.210 --> 04:31.540
I've only recently found out that she's Bai Xi.

04:31.810 --> 04:33.920
Why did Zhen Yu do this?

04:34.260 --> 04:35.280
I don't know.

04:36.159 --> 04:37.770
But Xi is innocent.

04:37.800 --> 04:38.880
She was deceived by Zhen Yu,

04:38.900 --> 04:40.530
which led her to commit many wrongdoings.

04:40.930 --> 04:42.900
She suffers from guilt now.

04:42.930 --> 04:44.080
Master,

04:44.100 --> 04:45.600
Xi was originally human.

04:45.860 --> 04:46.950
Please save her.

04:47.909 --> 04:49.100
Chong Zhao,

04:50.040 --> 04:52.200
Fu Ling has done too much evil.

04:52.220 --> 04:54.220
Even if she was once a human,

04:54.700 --> 04:56.090
after becoming a demon,

04:56.120 --> 04:58.770
everything she has done is her own doing.

04:59.610 --> 05:02.230
Moreover, she now carries demonic power.

05:02.250 --> 05:03.450
She has already become a demon.

05:03.480 --> 05:05.190
I cannot save her.

05:05.220 --> 05:05.930
Master...

05:05.950 --> 05:07.680
Because of her pitiful past,

05:07.710 --> 05:10.070
I won't kill her.

05:10.210 --> 05:11.210
But you can't

05:11.760 --> 05:13.250
ask for more.

05:14.250 --> 05:16.140
Eternals and demons walk different paths.

05:16.190 --> 05:18.310
You and she are ultimately different.

05:18.720 --> 05:20.960
Go back to Lanling with me.

05:29.050 --> 05:30.780
I can't return to Lanling anymore.

05:34.390 --> 05:35.830
Zhen Yu's demonic power

05:35.860 --> 05:38.030
has merged with my body.

05:39.300 --> 05:40.180
Master,

05:41.600 --> 05:43.040
I can't go back.

05:43.570 --> 05:45.040
Go back with me.

05:45.070 --> 05:47.390
I'll find a way to remove the demonic power within you.

05:47.409 --> 05:48.990
As you said,

05:49.010 --> 05:50.570
Eternals and demons walk different paths.

05:50.600 --> 05:52.480
Now, I'm neither an Eternal nor a demon.

05:52.500 --> 05:54.960
Returning to Lanling will only bring it trouble.

05:56.140 --> 05:58.190
Xi is all alone now.

05:59.140 --> 06:00.740
I want to stay here

06:01.020 --> 06:02.100
to be with her

06:02.720 --> 06:03.710
and protect her.

06:06.800 --> 06:08.810
Everything you've suffered

06:09.250 --> 06:10.940
has been for Lanling.

06:12.300 --> 06:13.740
In my heart,

06:14.100 --> 06:16.270
you'll always be my good disciple

06:17.920 --> 06:20.100
and a disciple of Lanling.

06:24.280 --> 06:26.180
Since you don't want to return,

06:27.160 --> 06:29.180
then stay here in Ning'an City.

06:29.390 --> 06:31.190
This place is your home after all.

06:31.220 --> 06:32.780
Go back

06:32.800 --> 06:34.040
when you come around.

06:34.630 --> 06:35.990
But...

06:36.930 --> 06:40.370
Fu Ling is no longer the Bai Xi she once was.

06:40.430 --> 06:42.750
Don't get too entangled with her.

06:42.780 --> 06:43.659
Otherwise...

06:46.730 --> 06:48.960
I've said all I need to say.

06:49.140 --> 06:51.270
Take care of yourself.

07:29.470 --> 07:30.500
My lord.

07:31.600 --> 07:33.600
This time it was my carelessness

07:33.909 --> 07:36.130
that caused the ancient mirror to shatter even further.

07:37.500 --> 07:38.900
But rest assured.

07:39.790 --> 07:42.040
I'll definitely capture Fan Yue

07:42.409 --> 07:43.920
and Bai Shuo

07:43.950 --> 07:45.990
at any cost

07:46.500 --> 07:48.310
to bring you back.

07:48.810 --> 07:50.170
As for Chong Zhao,

07:51.620 --> 07:53.940
he thinks he can escape everything

07:53.970 --> 07:55.490
with Fu Ling.

07:56.090 --> 07:57.770
He's too naive.

07:58.460 --> 08:01.160
He carries your hidden power.

08:01.520 --> 08:03.390
No matter where he is,

08:04.060 --> 08:06.850
I'll be able to find him.

08:09.020 --> 08:18.450
[Unbridled Pavilion]

08:11.690 --> 08:13.450
I want to go back to Ning'an City.

08:13.480 --> 08:14.890
With the fall of Cold Spring Palace,

08:14.920 --> 08:16.570
if Xi managed to escape,

08:16.600 --> 08:18.400
she'd definitely return to Ning'an City.

08:18.810 --> 08:20.840
Although I know the chances are slim,

08:20.870 --> 08:23.110
I still want to go back and wait there.

08:23.130 --> 08:24.130
What if she comes back?

08:24.160 --> 08:25.160
Tian Huo,

08:25.180 --> 08:26.330
you stay and guard Bright Moon Palace.

08:26.350 --> 08:27.470
But

08:27.550 --> 08:28.830
Master's condition...

08:28.860 --> 08:29.930
Don't worry.

08:30.120 --> 08:31.210
With me by his side,

08:31.680 --> 08:32.880
I'll protect him

08:32.909 --> 08:34.429
with my life.

08:37.980 --> 08:41.710
‚ôęThe person standing far away‚ôę

08:42.390 --> 08:44.660
‚ôęDon't be afraid‚ôę

08:45.220 --> 08:49.400
‚ôęThe stars will guide you to me‚ôę

08:46.970 --> 08:48.160
I'm Bai Shuo.

08:48.180 --> 08:49.580
I came with priceless treasures

08:49.610 --> 08:51.240
to meet your boss.

08:50.460 --> 08:57.100
‚ôęWalk towards me‚ôę

08:51.750 --> 08:52.990
You came to my turf

08:53.010 --> 08:54.350
to spout such nonsense.

08:55.190 --> 08:56.980
You've got some nerve.

08:58.700 --> 09:01.680
‚ôęMy heart feels so...‚ôę

08:59.110 --> 09:01.150
Since we are destined to meet,

09:01.150 --> 09:03.120
we should at least get to know each other.

09:02.260 --> 09:07.890
‚ôęIt's pounding as I wait for you‚ôę

09:03.300 --> 09:05.490
You have so much space in Unbridled Pavilion,

09:05.510 --> 09:06.960
and you're not doing business.

09:06.990 --> 09:08.780
It's a waste to leave it empty.

09:09.660 --> 09:13.960
‚ôęThe stars light up your eyes‚ôę

09:09.870 --> 09:10.410
I might as well use it for alchemy.

09:11.780 --> 09:12.510
I'm here

09:12.510 --> 09:14.520
to work for free in Unbridled Pavilion.

09:14.580 --> 09:16.500
I can do all the laundry and cooking.

09:16.530 --> 09:17.870
Just tell me what you want me to do.

09:17.560 --> 09:20.710
‚ôęYou are my distant call‚ôę

09:20.540 --> 09:21.740
What are you thinking about?

09:21.320 --> 09:25.980
‚ôęYou are my first and last‚ôę

09:22.010 --> 09:23.170
A lot of things.

09:24.320 --> 09:26.480
I'm thinking about the first time I came to Unbridled Pavilion.

09:26.420 --> 09:32.450
‚ôęMy heart is trembling for you‚ôę

09:27.090 --> 09:29.250
I'm thinking about our first meeting,

09:29.360 --> 09:31.250
about you teasing me,

09:31.640 --> 09:33.840
and also about Tian Huo and Cang Shan

09:32.770 --> 09:35.730
‚ôęIn this moment where we embrace each other‚ôę

09:34.010 --> 09:36.000
bickering here.

09:36.310 --> 09:40.190
‚ôęLet's never let go‚ôę

09:36.660 --> 09:37.980
And about Mu Jiu.

09:38.810 --> 09:41.260
Unbridled Pavilion used to be lively and bustling.

09:41.300 --> 09:43.730
I never thought it would be so quiet one day.

09:46.320 --> 09:47.320
Shuo,

09:48.780 --> 09:51.410
when everything is finally settled,

09:52.170 --> 09:53.720
we'll return to Unbridled Pavilion

09:54.870 --> 09:56.370
and reopen it.

09:58.980 --> 10:01.140
If only Xi could come back.

10:01.540 --> 10:03.260
We can definitely find her.

10:11.240 --> 10:12.450
Take a look.

10:12.510 --> 10:14.360
Fresh and good.

10:16.040 --> 10:17.280
Yeah, come on.

10:17.300 --> 10:18.060
Not bad.

10:18.430 --> 10:19.430
Take one.

10:28.030 --> 10:28.840
You're awake.

10:31.740 --> 10:32.930
I just made some steamed buns.

10:33.100 --> 10:33.940
Try one.

10:41.450 --> 10:42.950
As you said,

10:43.060 --> 10:44.610
Eternals and demons walk different paths.

10:44.850 --> 10:46.540
Now, I'm neither an Eternal nor a demon.

10:46.570 --> 10:48.690
Returning to Lanling will only bring it trouble.

10:49.540 --> 10:51.330
Xi is all alone now.

10:52.540 --> 10:53.990
I want to stay here

10:53.900 --> 10:56.760
‚ôęI remember that moonlit night‚ôę

10:54.510 --> 10:55.320
to be with her

10:56.060 --> 10:57.030
and protect her.

10:57.490 --> 10:59.400
Since you don't want to return,

10:57.600 --> 10:59.840
‚ôęThe flowers that bloomed once in a lifetime‚ôę

10:59.430 --> 11:01.660
then stay here in Ning'an City.

11:00.960 --> 11:04.520
‚ôęI remember that word of concern‚ôę

11:01.780 --> 11:03.630
This place is your home after all.

11:03.650 --> 11:05.170
Go back

11:05.200 --> 11:06.470
when you come around.

11:05.350 --> 11:08.190
‚ôęBut unfortunately, I didn't get to answer‚ôę

11:07.070 --> 11:08.070
But...

11:09.030 --> 11:12.230
Fu Ling is no longer the Bai Xi she once was.

11:09.090 --> 11:11.740
‚ôęI remember that drop of tear‚ôę

11:12.430 --> 11:14.880
Don't get too entangled with her.

11:12.660 --> 11:15.790
‚ôęIt dried in the wind‚ôę

11:14.900 --> 11:16.060
Otherwise...

11:16.500 --> 11:18.140
‚ôęThe one in the autumn wind‚ôę

11:16.750 --> 11:18.910
I've said all I need to say.

11:18.710 --> 11:22.030
‚ôęHow many times have I seen you in my dreams?‚ôę

11:19.170 --> 11:21.240
Take care of yourself.

11:23.050 --> 11:26.410
‚ôęThat year, that year‚ôę

11:27.120 --> 11:30.250
‚ôęThe leaves fell unnoticed after the flowers bloomed‚ôę

11:30.090 --> 11:31.380
Is it good?

11:30.910 --> 11:34.320
‚ôęI'm afraid the autumn wind will stir up memories‚ôę

11:31.710 --> 11:33.140
It's okay.

11:34.150 --> 11:35.610
Looks like I'm out of practice.

11:35.120 --> 11:37.580
‚ôęThey unfold, one page after another‚ôę

11:35.640 --> 11:37.450
I'll get the timing right tomorrow.

11:38.620 --> 11:41.900
‚ôęThat year, that year‚ôę

11:40.180 --> 11:41.480
I'm going out.

11:42.350 --> 11:43.400
Where are you going?

11:42.430 --> 11:45.400
‚ôęThe flowers flew under the moon, filling the sky‚ôę

11:43.540 --> 11:45.090
The poison in you hasn't been cured yet.

11:45.370 --> 11:46.900
I'm going to get some medicine for you.

11:46.330 --> 11:49.220
‚ôęFalling to the mud, burying the memories‚ôę

11:47.410 --> 11:48.440
You stay at home.

11:50.610 --> 11:52.620
‚ôęLayer after layer‚ôę

11:53.360 --> 11:56.190
‚ôęThat year, that year‚ôę

11:56.920 --> 11:59.590
‚ôęThe leaves fell unnoticed after the flowers bloomed‚ôę

12:00.490 --> 12:03.680
‚ôęI'm afraid the autumn wind will stir up memories‚ôę

12:01.170 --> 12:02.370
Xixi,

12:02.730 --> 12:04.420
if you were still alive,

12:04.740 --> 12:07.100
you'd definitely enjoy life here too.

12:04.870 --> 12:07.260
‚ôęThey unfold, one page after another‚ôę

12:08.440 --> 12:11.610
‚ôęThat year, that year‚ôę

12:09.140 --> 12:10.820
You always asked me

12:10.880 --> 12:12.880
why I was so good to Chong Zhao.

12:12.070 --> 12:15.330
‚ôęThe flowers flew under the moon, filling the sky‚ôę

12:13.370 --> 12:15.300
Now I finally understand.

12:15.940 --> 12:19.040
‚ôęFalling to the mud, burying the memories‚ôę

12:16.120 --> 12:18.660
It turns out I've fallen in love with him

12:18.780 --> 12:20.620
a long time ago.

12:20.290 --> 12:22.930
‚ôęLayer after layer‚ôę

12:22.890 --> 12:24.770
Unfortunately, I'm dying.

12:23.920 --> 12:27.190
‚ôęAnother year passed‚ôę

12:26.190 --> 12:28.950
I wish I had remembered him sooner.

12:38.460 --> 12:39.650
Unbridled Pavilion is open.

12:40.260 --> 12:41.780
Is Shuo back?

13:17.730 --> 13:20.060
Greetings, Divine Lord.

13:43.240 --> 13:44.600
After all the twists and turns,

13:44.620 --> 13:46.100
we're back in Unbridled Pavilion.

13:46.640 --> 13:47.950
I wonder what Fan Yue

13:47.970 --> 13:49.060
is doing now.

14:20.800 --> 14:22.120
Please.

14:22.120 --> 14:23.510
Please save Xi.

14:23.940 --> 14:26.270
If there truly are immortals in this world,

14:26.300 --> 14:28.270
please, save Xi.

14:28.290 --> 14:29.980
Souls destroyed.

14:30.230 --> 14:32.120
Eternal damnation.

14:32.480 --> 14:33.800
Those words

14:34.090 --> 14:35.680
were actually uttered

14:35.880 --> 14:37.800
by someone other than me.

14:38.540 --> 14:39.970
She's already dead.

14:40.000 --> 14:42.360
I never interfere with the life and death of any living being.

14:42.380 --> 14:43.400
Saving you

14:43.510 --> 14:44.960
was already an exception.

14:48.650 --> 14:50.450
The next time I descend to the mortal world,

14:50.480 --> 14:53.080
it may be thousands of years from now.

14:53.100 --> 14:54.050
You, a mortal,

14:54.120 --> 14:55.510
won't live beyond 100 years.

14:56.270 --> 14:58.840
How could you possibly repay me?

14:59.300 --> 15:00.610
Fan Yue.

15:09.900 --> 15:10.690
Shuo.

15:45.090 --> 15:46.450
I want you

15:47.940 --> 15:49.340
to repeat after me.

15:50.280 --> 15:51.960
Souls destroyed.

15:53.150 --> 15:54.630
Eternal damnation.

15:55.800 --> 15:56.600
Shuo,

15:56.670 --> 15:57.360
what's wrong with you?

15:57.360 --> 15:58.630
Repeat after me.

16:01.950 --> 16:03.190
Souls destroyed.

16:04.240 --> 16:05.480
Eternal damnation.

16:06.830 --> 16:08.520
Those words

16:09.110 --> 16:10.560
