16:53.760 --> 17:01.190
‚ôęWithstanding the stillness, you are a broken piece of me‚ôę

17:05.270 --> 17:08.829
‚ôęAcross thousands of miles‚ôę

17:08.829 --> 17:09.960
It was you.

17:11.710 --> 17:13.950
Not the person by the Lunar Hidden Sea.

17:13.599 --> 17:18.290
‚ôęThe pain of parting lingers‚ôę

17:15.380 --> 17:16.770
It was you.

17:20.920 --> 17:28.190
‚ôę I light a lamp with no wick to carry me through the rest of my days‚ôę

17:29.260 --> 17:33.930
‚ôęFlowers in the wind, sand in the water‚ôę

17:31.010 --> 17:32.140
Shuo.

17:32.650 --> 17:33.650
Have you remembered

17:33.680 --> 17:35.160
the person who saved you back then?

17:35.160 --> 17:36.310
It was you.

17:36.830 --> 17:38.990
Purple eyes and the purple moon.

17:39.620 --> 17:40.960
You saved me.

17:41.720 --> 17:42.720
He wasn't me.

17:43.520 --> 17:45.080
10 years ago, I was still Fan Yue.

17:45.100 --> 17:46.740
