18:01.780 --> 18:03.160
I don't know.

18:01.910 --> 18:07.370
‚ôęWhat kind of roots never turn into trees?‚ôę

18:04.290 --> 18:05.580
Just now,

18:05.830 --> 18:08.520
a few memories of Jing Yuan flashed through my mind.

18:09.170 --> 18:11.060
Maybe it's related to the purple moon's appearance.

18:10.410 --> 18:17.530
‚ôęTo break the roots of love, to look at the past and seal one's heart‚ôę

18:11.850 --> 18:13.610
