18:26.130 --> 18:27.610
You've always been searching for him.

18:26.950 --> 18:31.030
‚ôęThe flowers flew away‚ôę

18:29.540 --> 18:30.850
But Fan Yue,

18:32.070 --> 18:33.830
when the Demon Lord saved me back then,

18:34.380 --> 18:38.740
‚ôęMy tears are streaming down like rain‚ôę

18:34.670 --> 18:36.150
I was only 10 years old.

18:36.780 --> 18:38.610
I'm grateful to the Demon Lord, Jing Yuan,

18:39.680 --> 18:41.040
and have great respect

18:41.500 --> 18:42.610
for him,

18:42.660 --> 18:49.810
‚ôęLight my heart's lamp, cast away attachments, and ask the world‚ôę

18:43.490 --> 18:44.970
but that's all.

18:50.510 --> 18:52.130
The one I care about

18:50.810 --> 18:56.250
‚ôęOn the vast sea, you and I‚ôę

18:52.360 --> 18:53.200
and admire,

18:53.710 --> 18:55.190
the one I feel joy seeing

18:55.440 --> 18:57.360
and want to be with forever,

18:58.120 --> 18:59.160
is you,

18:59.860 --> 19:01.030
Fan Yue.

19:01.570 --> 19:03.470
‚ôęMay I ask, what do the gods see in the world?‚ôę

19:03.320 --> 19:04.760
I'm just so happy.

19:03.590 --> 19:05.420
‚ôęSadness from infatuation, anger, and parting‚ôę

19:05.570 --> 19:07.630
So happy that I finally found him.

19:05.630 --> 19:07.340
‚ôęMy love brought tears‚ôę

19:07.480 --> 19:09.380
‚ôęGreed for gathering, for holding, and for completeness‚ôę

19:07.750 --> 19:08.990
Do you understand?

19:09.770 --> 19:11.520
‚ôęI was never a flower, but I withered on my own‚ôę

19:11.760 --> 19:13.180
‚ôęI fell between your brows and became a good fruit‚ôę

19:13.410 --> 19:15.400
‚ôęBut I went through a thousand calamities for a promise‚ôę

19:15.840 --> 19:17.130
‚ôęI severed emotions, desires, and the fate between you and me‚ôę

19:17.690 --> 19:19.890
‚ôęTo protect the world for eternity‚ôę
Please bless the world‚ôęTo protect the world for eternity‚ôę

19:35.830 --> 19:36.980
Fu Ling.

19:37.000 --> 19:37.930
What's going on?

19:37.960 --> 19:39.290
Didn't you take the medicine?

19:39.320 --> 19:40.830
Why is your condition getting worse?

19:41.120 --> 19:42.510
I'll get you another bowl of decoction.

19:42.730 --> 19:43.770
No need.

19:43.800 --> 19:45.690
I just need to tough it out.

19:48.830 --> 19:50.720
Why has your condition worsened despite all the medicine you took?

19:51.710 --> 19:53.330
The medicine you took couldn't cure the poison,

19:53.350 --> 19:54.460
right?

19:54.490 --> 19:56.420
What kind of poison is in you?

19:57.350 --> 19:58.890
Stop asking.

19:58.910 --> 20:00.650
What the poison is

20:01.000 --> 20:02.730
is none of your concern.

20:02.930 --> 20:03.790
Fine.

20:04.170 --> 20:05.350
If you don't tell me,

20:05.680 --> 20:07.470
I'll go ask Zhen Yu.

20:07.590 --> 20:08.480
No!

20:09.680 --> 20:11.200
He'll kill you.

20:12.610 --> 20:14.100
Then tell me

20:14.130 --> 20:15.350
what the poison is

20:15.350 --> 20:16.480
and how we can cure it!

20:17.690 --> 20:19.260
Heart Devouring Poison.

20:20.060 --> 20:22.060
It was created by Zhen Yu.

20:22.090 --> 20:23.330
Except him,

20:23.350 --> 20:24.800
no one else can cure it.

20:24.830 --> 20:26.790
Normal medicine is useless.

20:27.330 --> 20:29.030
Shuo has already returned to Ning'an City.

20:29.310 --> 20:30.390
She can make pills.

20:30.980 --> 20:32.380
I'll take you to Unbridled Pavilion to find her.

20:32.410 --> 20:33.140
Maybe she can save you.

20:33.160 --> 20:33.880
No!

20:33.910 --> 20:35.020
I don't want to see her!

20:35.170 --> 20:36.300
Xi!

20:40.060 --> 20:41.060
Xi.

20:54.390 --> 20:57.150
It's okay. It's okay.

21:15.710 --> 21:17.200
I can't...

21:17.940 --> 21:19.920
I can't see Shuo.

21:20.320 --> 21:21.630
I've sinned.

21:22.010 --> 21:23.530
I can't see her.

21:24.790 --> 21:26.480
I can't see Shuo.

21:27.110 --> 21:28.270
I've sinned.

21:29.630 --> 21:31.110
I can't see her.

21:31.680 --> 21:32.760
I can't.

21:33.400 --> 21:35.530
When we first found the Lunar Hidden Sea,

21:36.860 --> 21:39.210
I saw a pendant on that person.

21:40.270 --> 21:41.920
It was identical to the one the Demon Lord

21:41.960 --> 21:43.960
was wearing when he saved me 10 years ago.

21:44.720 --> 21:47.000
So I thought he was the one who saved me.

21:47.870 --> 21:49.970
It turns out I was wrong all this time.

21:50.680 --> 21:52.770
But when I went to the Lunar Hidden Sea for the second time,

21:52.790 --> 21:54.630
why didn't he deny it?

21:55.220 --> 21:56.150
By the way,

21:56.170 --> 21:57.810
the pendant had a design

21:57.830 --> 21:59.280
of the moon and fire.

21:59.640 --> 22:01.320
In the memories you recalled,

22:01.340 --> 22:02.780
did you ever see him?

22:03.630 --> 22:04.640
No.

22:05.580 --> 22:06.880
Do you think

22:08.270 --> 22:10.920
he might be connected to the Demon Lord?

22:11.250 --> 22:13.010
Who exactly is he?

22:13.840 --> 22:15.680
Why was he by the Lunar Hidden Sea?

22:15.920 --> 22:17.850
What did those words

22:18.840 --> 22:20.530
he said to me mean?

22:22.690 --> 22:25.690
There are still many things I don't understand.

22:26.320 --> 22:28.230
Since he told you to activate the Contemplation Stone,

22:29.270 --> 22:30.470
after we collect the Five Contemplations,

22:30.500 --> 22:31.780
we may meet him again.

22:32.660 --> 22:34.580
Everything will make sense then.

22:54.130 --> 22:55.990
The tides of the Lunar Hidden Sea have ebbed and flowed for tens of thousands of years,

22:56.020 --> 22:57.540
creating some crystals.

22:58.810 --> 23:00.770
I found them interesting and collected them.

23:01.370 --> 23:03.240
You don't like jewelry,

23:03.300 --> 23:04.870
but this is made of stone.

23:04.950 --> 23:06.710
Divine Lord, you won't refuse it, will you?

23:09.270 --> 23:10.140
Who is she?

23:11.240 --> 23:12.640
What is my relationship

23:12.980 --> 23:14.420
with her?

23:27.100 --> 23:28.020
Shuo.

23:28.570 --> 23:29.400
Shuo!

23:30.400 --> 23:31.290
Shuo!

23:33.430 --> 23:34.430
Shuo.

23:35.830 --> 23:36.420
She's been poisoned,

23:36.440 --> 23:37.440
suffering unbearable pain every day.

23:37.470 --> 23:38.790
Do you have any pills to ease her pain?

23:42.000 --> 23:43.270
Fu Ling?

23:45.870 --> 23:46.900
You can't kill her!

23:46.930 --> 23:47.900
She's defected from Cold Spring Palace

23:47.930 --> 23:49.380
and no longer serves Zhen Yu.

23:49.400 --> 23:51.670
What does her defection have to do with me?

23:51.700 --> 23:52.950
All I know is I must avenge my father

23:52.970 --> 23:54.850
and the people of Ning'an City!

23:55.870 --> 23:57.480
But she knows where Xi is.

24:00.430 --> 24:01.490
Where is Bai Xi?

24:04.370 --> 24:05.790
Put me down.

24:08.660 --> 24:10.720
I told you I wouldn't come to Unbridled Pavilion.

24:10.750 --> 24:12.510
I told you I wouldn't beg her.

24:12.530 --> 24:14.250
Why did you still bring me here?

24:16.210 --> 24:17.430
Make it clear.

24:17.860 --> 24:19.150
Where is Bai Xi?

24:20.800 --> 24:22.560
Since you know where Bai Xi is,

24:23.750 --> 24:24.990
just tell her.

24:27.430 --> 24:28.280
Yes,

24:29.080 --> 24:30.880
I do know where Bai Xi is.

24:33.080 --> 24:34.760
Bai Xi is already dead.

24:35.700 --> 24:37.610
That weak, useless girl

24:37.670 --> 24:39.530
didn't even have the courage to hold a knife.

24:39.620 --> 24:41.890
She died the very first day

24:42.190 --> 24:43.860
she came to Cold Spring Palace.

24:46.820 --> 24:48.190
Impossible.

24:49.040 --> 24:50.240
Xi was gentle,

24:50.410 --> 24:51.880
but she was never weak.

24:52.520 --> 24:54.100
She wouldn't have died just like that.

24:54.670 --> 24:55.720
You're lying to me.

24:55.740 --> 24:57.210
You're definitely lying to me!

24:57.240 --> 24:59.050
Tell me where Xi is!

25:02.570 --> 25:03.360
Fu Ling.

25:03.760 --> 25:04.560
Fu Ling!

25:05.330 --> 25:06.130
Shuo.

25:07.130 --> 25:07.930
Save her.

25:23.480 --> 25:25.520
Now that Zhen Yu has fled with injuries,

25:25.800 --> 25:27.560
you don't have to stay in Cold Spring Palace anymore.

25:28.320 --> 25:29.350
I don't know why

25:29.350 --> 25:31.060
you're still entangled with Fu Ling,

25:31.270 --> 25:31.960
nor do I care about

25:31.960 --> 25:33.720
whatever ties you two have.

25:33.830 --> 25:36.630
But giving her the pill is my biggest compromise.

25:37.310 --> 25:38.420
Take her away.

25:38.440 --> 25:39.290
Shuo.

25:40.720 --> 25:41.900
Lately,

25:42.870 --> 25:45.280
I often think about the days when we were little‚ÄĒ

25:45.300 --> 25:47.020
you, me,

25:47.880 --> 25:49.050
and Xi.

25:51.720 --> 25:53.870
I know Xi had been to Cold Spring Palace,

25:54.980 --> 25:57.090
but Tian Huo went there to search

25:57.480 --> 25:58.980
and didn't find her.

25:59.490 --> 26:01.050
No one knows where she is.

26:03.090 --> 26:04.530
She says Xi is dead,

26:05.330 --> 26:06.770
but can I really believe her?

26:07.880 --> 26:09.160
She's killed so many people

26:09.160 --> 26:10.080
and done so many evil things.

26:10.110 --> 26:11.790
-Actually, Fu Ling is...
-She even caused my father's death!

26:12.850 --> 26:14.450
So, Chong Zhao, tell me.

26:14.470 --> 26:16.020
She said Xi is dead.

26:16.470 --> 26:17.580
Can I believe her?

26:18.950 --> 26:19.810
Shuo.

26:20.580 --> 26:21.620
I'm just like you.

26:21.720 --> 26:23.000
I really want to find Xi too.

26:23.400 --> 26:24.480
But there are many things

26:24.510 --> 26:25.880
I can't give you answers for.

26:27.570 --> 26:29.740
I've always felt that you're smarter than me,

26:29.760 --> 26:31.490
that you see things more clearly.

26:31.960 --> 26:33.240
Back then,

26:33.260 --> 26:35.780
my parents and I came to Ning'an City and opened a steamed bun stall.

26:36.050 --> 26:37.890
At first, I really didn't understand it.

26:37.930 --> 26:39.520
We were Eternals

26:39.850 --> 26:41.240
with the power to summon wind and rain,

26:41.270 --> 26:42.430
change shapes, and move things at will.

26:42.460 --> 26:44.140
Yet, we had to hide our identities,

26:44.160 --> 26:45.430
suppress our power,

26:45.650 --> 26:48.410
and spend every day just making and selling steamed buns.

26:48.880 --> 26:50.680
Why couldn't we fight back when we were bullied

26:50.680 --> 26:51.600
and mistreated?

26:51.630 --> 26:53.320
Instead, we had to swallow our pride and endure.

26:55.200 --> 26:56.000
During that time,

26:56.000 --> 26:57.770
I argued with my parents every day.

26:58.040 --> 26:59.630
And they scolded me every day.

27:00.330 --> 27:01.610
At that time,

27:02.190 --> 27:03.520
I wasn't happy.

27:11.930 --> 27:13.740
If you're feeling really down,

27:13.770 --> 27:15.200
why not have a good sleep

27:15.220 --> 27:16.450
and dream a good dream?

27:16.560 --> 27:18.520
When you wake up, it'll be a brand new day.

27:40.450 --> 27:42.000
The sun is shining brightly today,

27:42.020 --> 27:43.390
with a gentle, warm breeze.

27:43.740 --> 27:45.310
When you're in a bad mood,

27:45.330 --> 27:47.040
just soak up the sun.

28:05.860 --> 28:07.870
The pear blossoms are in full bloom outside the city.

28:07.900 --> 28:08.900
They're beautiful.

28:08.920 --> 28:10.120
Take a trip when you have time.

28:10.150 --> 28:11.840
It'll help you forget a lot of worries.

28:16.620 --> 28:18.390
[In the early morning mist, the riverbank is shrouded in light rain, with willow trees looking like a painting.]

28:47.540 --> 28:48.540
At that time,

28:48.570 --> 28:50.130
I often delivered steamed buns to your house,

28:50.620 --> 28:52.060
so I recognized

28:52.490 --> 28:53.810
that the sachet belonged to you.

28:54.330 --> 28:55.430
Here, Xi.

29:03.740 --> 29:05.140
If it weren't for you,

29:05.520 --> 29:07.840
I would've wallowed in it for a long time.

29:08.120 --> 29:09.400
I'm really thankful

29:09.420 --> 29:11.520
for the comfort you brought me back then.

29:12.020 --> 29:13.640
Now, I want to

29:14.650 --> 29:16.160
return this sachet to you.

29:16.610 --> 29:18.690
I never wrote you any notes.

29:19.550 --> 29:20.770
It wasn't me

29:21.350 --> 29:22.160
who comforted you.

29:22.790 --> 29:23.720
But this sachet...

29:23.720 --> 29:25.110
It was indeed mine,

29:25.640 --> 29:27.530
but not long after, I gave it to Xi.

29:28.300 --> 29:30.410
Could the one who sent you notes to comfort you

29:30.440 --> 29:31.730
have been Xi?

29:34.490 --> 29:35.910
I remember there was a time

29:36.000 --> 29:38.080
when she would sneak out by herself.

29:38.100 --> 29:39.220
When I asked her where she was going,

29:39.260 --> 29:40.770
she wouldn't tell me.

29:40.860 --> 29:43.300
It seems she was going to find you.

29:45.870 --> 29:47.550
But I recognize your handwriting.

29:47.630 --> 29:49.390
Xi taught me how to write.

29:49.920 --> 29:51.890
I learned to write by copying her characters.

29:51.910 --> 29:53.180
Naturally, our handwritings look similar.

29:53.610 --> 29:55.700
If you want to know what really happened back then,

29:55.720 --> 29:57.350
you'll have to find Xi

29:57.480 --> 29:58.500
and ask her.

29:59.010 --> 30:01.620
I don't believe Xi could have died like that.

30:02.550 --> 30:04.090
Even if Fu Ling refuses to tell me,

30:04.670 --> 30:07.030
I'll find Xi my own way.

30:07.770 --> 30:09.250
As for Fu Ling,

30:10.140 --> 30:11.940
just because she has betrayed Cold Spring Palace

30:11.960 --> 30:14.400
doesn't mean the evil she's done can be erased.

30:15.170 --> 30:16.160
For your sake,

30:16.160 --> 30:18.510
I'll show her mercy and won't kill her,

30:19.430 --> 30:20.670
but I won't save her.

30:21.440 --> 30:22.330
Take her away.

30:24.540 --> 30:25.580
Shuo.

31:24.350 --> 31:27.040
The Contemplation Stone lives up to its reputation as the divine object of Goddess Xing Yue.

31:27.620 --> 31:30.210
Its power has wounded me so badly.

31:30.570 --> 31:32.350
To repair the ancient mirror,

31:32.380 --> 31:34.710
I need more power.

31:37.340 --> 31:38.310
If back then,

31:38.310 --> 31:40.400
that idiot turtle from Lanling hadn't deceived me,

31:41.020 --> 31:43.910
I wouldn't have wasted so many years

31:43.940 --> 31:45.400
and lost the opportunity.

31:46.680 --> 31:48.810
Old Turtle,

31:48.840 --> 31:50.620
you brought this upon yourself.

31:50.910 --> 31:52.780
I will never let you off the hook.

31:57.180 --> 31:58.220
Fan Yue.

31:58.810 --> 32:00.290
What's wrong with you?

32:01.720 --> 32:02.680
I'm fine.

32:02.710 --> 32:03.730
You're lying.

32:04.750 --> 32:06.110
You've been acting weird today,

32:06.140 --> 32:07.730
like you're purposely avoiding me.

32:07.750 --> 32:08.510
We're so close now.

32:08.540 --> 32:10.540
You can tell me anything.

32:18.810 --> 32:20.340
This is my master's turtle shell.

32:20.720 --> 32:21.850
Master once said

32:21.880 --> 32:23.190
he has many turtle shells,

32:23.210 --> 32:24.750
but this one is always with him.

32:24.930 --> 32:26.370
Now that he's sent it over,

32:26.400 --> 32:27.530
something must have happened.

32:27.550 --> 32:28.810
Old Turtle has always been in Lanling.

32:28.840 --> 32:30.300
There have been no reports of an attack on Lanling.

32:37.090 --> 32:38.400
The turtle shell is giving us a direction.

32:40.960 --> 32:41.810
The east.

32:49.850 --> 32:50.920
Shuo said those things

32:50.920 --> 32:52.340
because she didn't know who you were.

32:52.500 --> 32:53.890
She's been searching for you for many years.

32:53.920 --> 32:55.600
Don't you want to be reunited with your sister?

32:59.090 --> 33:00.460
The one she's been looking for

33:00.480 --> 33:02.150
is her sister, Bai Xi.

33:02.180 --> 33:04.120
But look at me now.

33:04.370 --> 33:05.540
My hands are covered in blood,

33:05.570 --> 33:06.720
and I've done too many bad things.

33:06.740 --> 33:08.180
What right do I have to be Bai Xi again?

33:08.480 --> 33:09.720
I'd rather she think

33:09.720 --> 33:11.070
Bai Xi is dead.

33:11.460 --> 33:12.030
But‚Ä¶

33:12.030 --> 33:13.790
I don't want to talk about this anymore.

33:14.600 --> 33:16.010
Then what about us?

33:19.650 --> 33:21.770
The one who sent me notes back then was you,

33:22.000 --> 33:23.050
right?

33:23.390 --> 33:25.020
I don't want to talk about that either.

33:25.900 --> 33:27.990
If you're feeling really down,

33:28.880 --> 33:30.270
why not have a good sleep

33:30.550 --> 33:31.790
and dream a good dream?

33:34.090 --> 33:35.930
When you wake up, it'll be a brand new day.

33:40.470 --> 33:42.340
The sun is shining brightly today,

33:42.060 --> 33:44.920
‚ôęI remember that moonlit night‚ôę

33:42.370 --> 33:43.740
with a gentle, warm breeze.

33:45.120 --> 33:46.510
When you're in a bad mood,

33:45.760 --> 33:48.300
‚ôęThe flowers that bloomed once in a lifetime‚ôę

33:46.510 --> 33:47.720
just soak up the sun.

33:48.770 --> 33:50.900
The pear blossoms are in full bloom outside the city.

33:49.120 --> 33:52.290
‚ôęI remember that word of concern‚ôę

33:51.150 --> 33:52.560
They're beautiful.

33:52.940 --> 33:54.780
Take a trip when you have time.

33:53.200 --> 33:56.130
‚ôęBut unfortunately, I didn't get to answer‚ôę

33:55.420 --> 33:57.420
It'll help you forget a lot of worries.

33:56.660 --> 33:59.480
‚ôęI remember that drop of tear‚ôę

33:57.660 --> 33:59.380
Enough! Stop reciting them.

33:59.410 --> 34:01.340
They were just some casual things I wrote.

34:00.480 --> 34:03.440
‚ôęIt dried in the wind‚ôę

34:01.360 --> 34:02.400
I've long forgotten them.

34:04.450 --> 34:05.780
‚ôęThe one in the autumn wind‚ôę

34:06.740 --> 34:10.350
‚ôęHow many times have I seen you in my dreams?‚ôę

34:11.320 --> 34:14.429
‚ôęThat year, that year‚ôę

34:12.060 --> 34:14.020
Then, will these remind you?

34:14.139 --> 34:16.260
I've kept every single one of those notes.

34:14.790 --> 34:17.179
[The afterglow paints the rooftops and drifting smoke golden.]

34:14.790 --> 34:17.179
[When you're bored, you can go to the riverbank to look at the sunset.]

34:15.100 --> 34:18.219
‚ôęThe leaves fell unnoticed after the flowers bloomed‚ôę

34:16.280 --> 34:17.639
Over the years,

34:17.670 --> 34:19.670
I've read them again and again.

34:18.860 --> 34:22.239
‚ôęI'm afraid the autumn wind will stir up memories‚ôę

34:19.969 --> 34:22.370
I always thought the person from back then was Shuo,

34:22.520 --> 34:24.520
and I've kept her in my heart ever since,

34:22.949 --> 34:25.570
‚ôęThey unfold, one page after another‚ôę

34:25.120 --> 34:27.560
treasuring and loving her.

34:26.340 --> 34:29.670
‚ôęThat year, that year‚ôę

34:28.690 --> 34:30.010
But it turns out

34:30.230 --> 34:32.820
I was wrong from the start.

34:30.429 --> 34:33.429
‚ôęThe flowers flew under the moon, filling the sky‚ôę

34:33.310 --> 34:35.020
I liked Shuo

34:34.150 --> 34:37.239
‚ôęFalling to the mud, burying the memories‚ôę

34:35.590 --> 34:37.500
because I was touched by these notes,

34:37.330 --> 34:39.719
[The afterglow paints the rooftops and drifting smoke golden.]

34:37.330 --> 34:39.719
[When you're bored, you can go to the riverband to look at the sunset.]

34:37.530 --> 34:38.860
these comforting words.

34:38.310 --> 34:41.060
‚ôęLayer after layer‚ôę

34:39.650 --> 34:41.690
But the encouragement and company back then

34:41.929 --> 34:45.900
‚ôęAnother year passed‚ôę

34:42.520 --> 34:44.239
were actually from you.

34:48.710 --> 34:50.630
I've been such a fool.

34:52.120 --> 34:52.840
For all these years,

34:52.840 --> 34:55.030
I didn't even know I liked the wrong person.

34:55.489 --> 34:56.699
I told you,

34:57.130 --> 34:58.330
I've already forgotten.

34:57.770 --> 35:01.020
‚ôęI remember that moonlit night‚ôę

34:58.360 --> 34:59.800
You indeed once forgot.

35:01.470 --> 35:04.200
‚ôęThe flowers that bloomed once in a lifetime‚ôę

35:01.560 --> 35:03.890
Zhen Yu erased all your memories.

35:04.160 --> 35:06.350
But even when you couldn't remember anything,

35:04.830 --> 35:08.270
‚ôęI remember that word of concern‚ôę

35:06.380 --> 35:08.380
you still showed me mercy and protected me.

35:09.180 --> 35:11.330
It was because your heart never changed.

35:09.220 --> 35:12.030
‚ôęBut unfortunately, I didn't get to answer‚ôę

35:12.080 --> 35:13.330
What are you trying to prove

35:12.960 --> 35:15.490
‚ôęI remember that drop of tear‚ôę

35:13.720 --> 35:15.190
by saying all this?

35:15.810 --> 35:16.560
Yes,

35:16.530 --> 35:19.670
‚ôęIt dried in the wind‚ôę

35:17.560 --> 35:19.040
after losing my memories,

35:19.070 --> 35:20.800
I became ruthless to everyone,

35:20.330 --> 35:21.840
‚ôęThe one in the autumn wind‚ôę

35:20.820 --> 35:21.940
except you.

35:22.780 --> 35:26.390
‚ôęHow many times have I seen you in my dreams?‚ôę

35:22.840 --> 35:24.770
I had a special feeling about you.

35:27.160 --> 35:28.440
But Chong Zhao,

35:27.430 --> 35:30.210
‚ôęThat year, that year‚ôę

35:28.770 --> 35:31.330
you're an Eternal, and I've become a demon,

35:31.060 --> 35:34.140
‚ôęThe leaves fell unnoticed after the flowers bloomed‚ôę

35:31.350 --> 35:32.750
a demon who committed countless sins.

35:33.400 --> 35:35.210
There's no future between us.

35:34.840 --> 35:38.050
‚ôęI'm afraid the autumn wind will stir up memories‚ôę

35:35.230 --> 35:36.910
I also have demonic power now,

35:38.200 --> 35:39.540
and my hands are stained

35:39.080 --> 35:41.530
‚ôęThey unfold, one page after another‚ôę

35:40.080 --> 35:41.590
with the blood of Eternals too.

35:41.610 --> 35:42.570
That was forced upon you!

35:42.450 --> 35:45.590
‚ôęThat year, that year‚ôę

35:42.600 --> 35:43.850
Wasn't it the same for you?

35:45.480 --> 35:47.000
You were a 12-year-old girl

35:46.190 --> 35:49.400
‚ôęThe flowers flew under the moon, filling the sky‚ôę

35:47.020 --> 35:49.020
who was always gentle and kind

35:49.510 --> 35:51.240
and wouldn't even hurt a fly.

35:50.200 --> 35:53.230
‚ôęFalling to the mud, burying the memories‚ôę

35:51.260 --> 35:52.740
But suddenly, your memories were erased,

35:52.770 --> 35:53.770
and you were thrown into fights

35:53.790 --> 35:55.020
in Cold Spring Palace.

35:54.490 --> 35:56.950
‚ôęLayer after layer‚ôę

35:57.120 --> 35:58.600
What choice did you have?

35:58.030 --> 36:01.600
‚ôęAnother year passed‚ôę

35:59.520 --> 36:00.880
How could you have survived otherwise?

36:14.180 --> 36:15.220
Xi.

36:16.630 --> 36:17.900
Can you let me

36:16.760 --> 36:19.680
‚ôęThat year, that year‚ôę

36:19.000 --> 36:20.560
stay by your side,

36:20.040 --> 36:23.040
‚ôęThe leaves fell unnoticed after the flowers bloomed‚ôę

36:21.090 --> 36:22.400
protect you,

36:23.820 --> 36:25.420
and watch out for you?

36:23.960 --> 36:27.240
‚ôęI'm afraid the autumn wind will stir up memories‚ôę

36:25.990 --> 36:27.540
Can you give us a chance

36:28.340 --> 36:29.500
to start over?

36:28.400 --> 36:31.000
‚ôęThey unfold, one page after another‚ôę

36:31.840 --> 36:35.010
‚ôęThat year, that year‚ôę

36:35.500 --> 36:38.680
‚ôęThe flowers flew under the moon, filling the sky‚ôę

36:38.070 --> 36:39.320
Chong Zhao.

36:39.440 --> 36:42.520
‚ôęFalling to the mud, burying the memories‚ôę

36:40.960 --> 36:41.960
I...

36:43.880 --> 36:45.280
What's wrong with you?

36:43.990 --> 36:46.490
‚ôęLayer after layer‚ôę

36:47.440 --> 36:50.740
‚ôęAnother year passed‚ôę

36:48.320 --> 36:49.280
What's wrong with you?

36:58.400 --> 36:59.410
Lady Xi,

36:59.580 --> 37:01.100
there are hibiscus flowers in the city too.

37:01.120 --> 37:03.100
Why did you come all the way out here so early

37:03.150 --> 37:04.310
to pick them?

37:04.340 --> 37:05.280
Shuo and Zhao

37:05.280 --> 37:07.000
love the hibiscus cakes I make.

37:07.000 --> 37:08.760
The flowers here are the most vibrant,

37:08.760 --> 37:10.180
so naturally, I came here to pick them.

37:10.200 --> 37:10.950
Lingdang.

37:10.980 --> 37:12.350
Go gather some dew.

37:12.400 --> 37:13.910
Making the cakes with the morning dew

37:13.930 --> 37:15.160
makes them the sweetest.

37:15.190 --> 37:16.390
Yes, Lady Xi.

37:29.010 --> 37:30.200
Aunt Meng!

37:30.660 --> 37:31.950
Let me help you up.

37:33.530 --> 37:34.490
What happened to you?

37:34.520 --> 37:35.810
Why are you bleeding so much?

37:35.840 --> 37:36.920
Xi.

37:37.940 --> 37:39.270
Hurry home.

37:42.030 --> 37:44.000
Give this to Chong Zhao.

37:44.020 --> 37:45.430
Tell him‚Ä¶

37:44.490 --> 37:46.320
[Follow the way of heaven as the way. Practice kindness, caution, and harmony.]

37:45.640 --> 37:46.380
Don't...

37:46.410 --> 37:48.210
Don't ever return to Lanling.

37:48.230 --> 37:49.180
Go now.

37:49.330 --> 37:50.250
What's Lanling?

37:50.280 --> 37:51.280
I don't understand.

37:51.300 --> 37:52.090
Aunt Meng.

37:52.120 --> 37:54.000
Let me help you back home. Let's go.

37:54.030 --> 37:55.110
There's no time.

37:57.340 --> 37:58.380
Go!

38:08.140 --> 38:09.090
Father.

38:09.120 --> 38:11.000
I'll go ask Father to save Aunt Meng.

38:33.300 --> 38:34.350
Xi.

38:34.740 --> 38:36.100
Xi, what's wrong?

38:37.760 --> 38:38.760
Chong Zhao.

38:39.790 --> 38:40.990
Your parents

38:41.010 --> 38:42.620
weren't killed by a scorpion demon.

38:44.010 --> 38:45.630
Before your mother died,

38:45.980 --> 38:47.350
I met her.

38:49.270 --> 38:50.230
What are you saying?

38:51.030 --> 38:52.690
I couldn't see the person's face clearly,

38:53.000 --> 38:55.240
but I vaguely saw that he severely injured your mother.

38:55.270 --> 38:56.680
He also tried to kill me,

38:56.700 --> 38:58.780
but I lost consciousness soon.

38:58.830 --> 39:00.110
I don't know

39:00.140 --> 39:01.340
what happened after that.

39:01.360 --> 39:02.700
Don't return to Lanling?

39:03.290 --> 39:05.520
Was she hunted down by someone from Lanling?

39:05.580 --> 39:06.580
No.

39:06.610 --> 39:08.040
I must go back to tell Master

39:08.060 --> 39:09.340
and have him look into it.

39:09.370 --> 39:10.450
No.

39:10.470 --> 39:11.990
You can't trust anyone in Lanling.

39:12.020 --> 39:14.270
Your master could also be the one who killed your mother.

39:14.290 --> 39:15.250
Impossible.

39:15.970 --> 39:18.020
My master and my parents had a deep bond.

39:18.040 --> 39:19.000
If it were my master,

39:19.030 --> 39:20.610
he wouldn't have raised me himself.

39:21.010 --> 39:23.120
Anyone in this world might hurt me,

39:23.140 --> 39:24.490
but my master would never.

39:24.520 --> 39:25.440
Moreover,

39:25.460 --> 39:27.270
my master has been protecting people his whole life.

39:27.300 --> 39:29.090
He would never do such a thing.

39:34.490 --> 39:37.420
[Bodhi Village]

39:41.650 --> 39:43.690
The compass led us here.

39:43.720 --> 39:44.950
Is my master

39:44.970 --> 39:46.510
in this village?

39:46.610 --> 39:48.380
Do you know this village?

39:48.960 --> 39:51.290
I've never heard of such a place on the Eastern Continent.

39:53.120 --> 39:55.200
But the compass is clearly pointing towards the village.

39:55.220 --> 39:56.570
Why don't we go in and have a look?

39:56.870 --> 39:58.230
A single village,

39:58.400 --> 39:59.770
hidden in the mountains.

39:59.790 --> 40:00.500
It's rather strange.

40:01.180 --> 40:02.380
Stay close to me after going in.

40:03.170 --> 40:04.290
Let's go.

40:07.320 --> 40:08.510
Here, take it if you like.

40:08.560 --> 40:09.600
-Old wine.
-Pumpkins.

40:09.630 --> 40:10.720
Fresh pumpkins.

40:10.740 --> 40:12.050
Take one with you.

40:12.430 --> 40:13.950
-Take a look.
-Take one. Take one.

40:14.400 --> 40:15.290
So fresh.

40:19.620 --> 40:20.910
Thank you, sir.

40:21.510 --> 40:22.150
It smells so good.

40:23.450 --> 40:25.140
Why are there humans

40:25.170 --> 40:26.480
on the land of the Eternals?

40:26.500 --> 40:27.750
They all have mana.

40:28.180 --> 40:28.970
They're not humans.

40:31.600 --> 40:33.200
This village is not simple.

40:33.220 --> 40:34.320
Be cautious.

40:36.360 --> 40:37.110
Come look.

40:37.110 --> 40:38.340
Miss, take a look.

40:43.100 --> 40:45.110
Have a look. Fresh fruit.

40:45.130 --> 40:46.820
Miss, come back again.

40:46.850 --> 40:47.520
Thank you, madam.

40:47.540 --> 40:49.060
Sir, the wontons are really good.

40:49.110 --> 40:50.510
I'll pack some for you.

40:50.770 --> 40:51.520
Take care.

40:51.780 --> 40:52.790
Sir.

40:53.420 --> 40:54.630
We were out for a walk

40:54.660 --> 40:55.700
and stumbled upon this place.

40:56.110 --> 40:57.110
May I ask where this is?

40:57.110 --> 40:58.230
This is Bodhi Village.

40:58.230 --> 40:59.650
You're here because you're meant to be.

40:59.670 --> 41:01.020
Welcome.

41:01.160 --> 41:01.990
Meant to be?

41:02.010 --> 41:02.660
Yes.

41:02.690 --> 41:04.440
This village is protected by the Divine Maiden.

41:04.510 --> 41:05.510
Whether you're on the run,

41:05.510 --> 41:06.550
homeless,

41:06.550 --> 41:07.810
or seeking to avoid the mundane world,

41:07.840 --> 41:08.760
if fate brings you here,

41:08.800 --> 41:09.960
the Divine Maiden will take you in,

41:09.990 --> 41:10.800
never asking about your past

41:10.800 --> 41:11.640
and treating everyone equally.

41:11.670 --> 41:12.500
The Divine Maiden?

41:12.520 --> 41:13.850
That's right. This village

41:13.880 --> 41:15.320
owes everything to the Divine Maiden.

41:14.200 --> 41:17.020
[Food]

41:15.360 --> 41:16.920
We were all saved by her.

41:16.920 --> 41:17.710
Yes.

41:17.710 --> 41:19.670
The Divine Maiden is not only powerful

41:19.670 --> 41:21.510
but also very compassionate.

41:21.690 --> 41:22.770
She's the kindest person

41:22.790 --> 41:24.620
in the world.

41:24.650 --> 41:26.010
If you meet her,

41:26.030 --> 41:27.510
you'll definitely like her too.

41:27.550 --> 41:28.280
Definitely, you'll like her.

41:28.280 --> 41:28.840
Yes.

41:28.860 --> 41:29.970
Yes, you will.

41:30.890 --> 41:32.530
Let's go over there.

41:35.920 --> 41:37.920
Do you think the Divine Maiden

41:37.950 --> 41:38.830
they spoke of is real?

41:38.850 --> 41:40.040
Whether real or not,

41:40.380 --> 41:41.980
someone who can hide so much spiritual energy

41:42.000 --> 41:43.080
and keep it a secret

41:43.640 --> 41:44.910
is definitely not an ordinary person.

41:47.820 --> 41:48.410
Look.

41:48.440 --> 41:49.400
The Divine Maiden is here!

41:51.630 --> 41:52.980
I told you,

41:53.010 --> 41:54.300
once you come to this village,

41:54.320 --> 41:55.880
we're all family.

41:55.900 --> 41:57.110
No need for formalities.

41:57.140 --> 41:59.170
Just do your own thing.

42:26.190 --> 42:27.460
Divine Maiden,

42:27.490 --> 42:28.220
you...

42:28.240 --> 42:29.590
I've finally found you.

42:47.170 --> 42:47.850
What...

42:47.870 --> 42:49.140
What's going on?

42:49.670 --> 42:50.750
I don't know.

42:50.770 --> 42:52.400
What's wrong with the Divine Maiden?

42:53.630 --> 42:54.500
Is he the one

42:54.520 --> 42:56.080
the Divine Maiden has been waiting for?

42:56.110 --> 42:57.400
No way.

42:57.420 --> 42:59.140
The Divine Maiden has been waiting for him all this time,

42:59.430 --> 43:00.320
but now he has

43:00.340 --> 43:02.170
another woman by his side.

43:05.280 --> 43:06.840
The Divine Maiden must be heartbroken.

43:07.730 --> 43:09.550
What does she mean?

43:11.050 --> 43:12.080
Do you two know each other?

43:18.820 --> 43:19.760
I've never met her.

43:20.650 --> 43:21.920
You don't remember me?

43:27.540 --> 43:29.530
Yeah, 60,000 years is so long

43:29.870 --> 43:30.750
that

43:30.780 --> 43:32.010
you've forgotten everything.

43:34.520 --> 43:35.770
It's okay.

43:34.570 --> 43:37.350
[Food]

43:35.800 --> 43:36.640
If you've forgotten me,

43:36.660 --> 43:38.090
we'll just get to know each other again.

43:38.790 --> 43:40.390
In scattered flowers and flying petals,

43:40.560 --> 43:42.250
my once youthful face has changed.

43:42.460 --> 43:44.110
Now, I go by the name

43:44.000 --> 43:45.330
[Luan Zhu, Divine Race]

43:44.140 --> 43:45.140
Luan Zhu.

43:53.630 --> 43:55.100
Ms. Luan Zhu,

43:55.120 --> 43:56.760
why not let me get to know you as well?

43:58.190 --> 43:59.440
You're a human?

43:59.690 --> 44:00.690
Yes.

44:00.710 --> 44:01.860
Bai Shuo, a human.

44:02.760 --> 44:03.760
It's getting late.

44:03.800 --> 44:05.370
I'll skip the pleasantries.

44:05.400 --> 44:06.590
We came to this village

44:06.670 --> 44:08.000
to look for someone.

44:08.360 --> 44:10.520
Have there been any other visitors besides us

44:10.540 --> 44:12.150
in the past several days?

44:13.750 --> 44:14.500
Well...

44:16.570 --> 44:17.870
Shuo!
